"{\"uid\": \"aljazeera.com-news-2024-8-2-algerian-boxer-imane-khelif-becomes-target-of-gender-row-at-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The fighter under scrutiny won her opening bout when opponent Angela Carini from Italy quits after 46 seconds.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 110, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 62, \"end\": 75, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 81, \"end\": 86, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.998308846027173, \"rank\": 0.001038774761396434, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Share  Save  Algerian boxer Imane Khelif's 46-second victory at the Paris Olympics has ignited a heated debate over gender eligibility rules with global public figures and sporting bodies weighing in.\", \"from\": 112, \"to\": 312, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 125, \"end\": 133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999965222051735, \"rank\": 2.8787852303851284e-06, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 140, \"end\": 152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Italian boxer Angela Carini abandoned the match against Khelif on Thursday, walking away from the contest to her corner - an extremely rare scene in Olympic boxing.\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 314, \"end\": 321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9945497159191811, \"rank\": 0.0054514099907980096, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 328, \"end\": 341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carini did not shake Khelif's hand after the referee formally raised it.\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 480, \"end\": 486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999999971969373, \"rank\": 2.803112410885174e-09, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She cried in the ring, sinking to her knees.\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 597, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Minutes later, still-tearful, Carini said she quit because of the pain from opening punches.\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 628, \"end\": 634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999999971969373, \"rank\": 2.803112410885174e-09, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I felt a severe pain in my nose, and with the maturity of a boxer, I said 'enough' because I did not want to.\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 802, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not want to.\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 821, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not finish the match,\\\" Carini said.\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 865, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 853, \"end\": 859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999999971969373, \"rank\": 2.803112410885174e-09, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif was disqualified from the 2023 world championships after failing an unspecified gender eligibility test.\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 978, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her participation in the Paris Olympics has become a divisive issue.\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1047, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Author JK Rowling referred to her as a \\\"male\\\", accusing her of \\\"enjoying the distress of a woman he's just punched in the head, and whose life's ambition he's just shattered\\\".\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1056, \"end\": 1066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JK Rowling\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The writer has incurred the wrath of human rights activists in recent years over her stance, often in relation to transgender issues, that biological sex is immutable.\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Truth Social, United States presidential candidate Donald Trump declared in capital letters, \\\"I will keep men out of women's sports\\\" while his vice-presidential nominee, JD Vance, argued that \\\"Kamala Harris's ideas about gender\\\" have led \\\"to a grown man pummelling a woman in a boxing match\\\".\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1398, \"end\": 1410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Truth_Social\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Truth Social\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Truth_Social\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Truth_Social\"}, {\"begin\": 1412, \"end\": 1448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_United_States_presidential_election\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"United States presidential candidate\", \"types\": [\"Q40231\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_United_States_presidential_election\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_United_States_presidential_election\"}, {\"begin\": 1449, \"end\": 1461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.999999999994543, \"rank\": 5.408955001468158e-12, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 1568, \"end\": 1570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janata_Dal\", \"score\": 0.9772053931854661, \"rank\": 0.0120692735063452, \"text\": \"JD\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janata_Dal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janata_Dal\"}, {\"begin\": 1571, \"end\": 1576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"score\": 0.9999999966394171, \"rank\": 3.3607843157537468e-09, \"text\": \"Vance\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\"}, {\"begin\": 1591, \"end\": 1597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamala_Harris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7670106353509182e-22, \"text\": \"Kamala\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamala_Harris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamala_Harris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reem Alsalem, the United Nations special rapporteur on violence against women and girls, wrote on X that Carini \\\"and other female athletes should not have been exposed to this physical and psychological violence based on their sex\\\".\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1924, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1710, \"end\": 1743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations_special_rapporteur\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"United Nations special rapporteur\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations_special_rapporteur\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations_special_rapporteur\"}, {\"begin\": 1797, \"end\": 1803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999999971969373, \"rank\": 2.803112410885174e-09, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People would rather spread misinformation instead of simply doing cursory research.\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 2009, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The way these grifters and concern trolls are acting, you'd think Imane Khelif was just Mike Tysoning dainty women left and right.\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2076, \"end\": 2088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has NINE losses.\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2162, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was in the last Olympics and did not win\\u2026pic.twitter.com/iPvPpzt5CG  - Ibou, of WrestlePurists (@BackupHangman)August 1, 2024    Algerian officials and others sympathised with Khelif as she was targeted online.\", \"from\": 2163, \"to\": 2377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2296, \"end\": 2304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999965222051735, \"rank\": 2.8787852303851284e-06, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Algeria's Olympic Committee (COA) condemned what it called \\\"malicious and unethical attacks directed against our distinguished athlete, Imane Khelif, by certain foreign media\\\".\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2555, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2379, \"end\": 2386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999998750076962, \"rank\": 1.2418453359454314e-07, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 2515, \"end\": 2527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadia Whittome, a British politician, posted on X: \\\"Imane Khelif was assigned female at birth.\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2651, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2557, \"end\": 2571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadia_Whittome\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nadia Whittome\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadia_Whittome\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadia_Whittome\"}, {\"begin\": 2575, \"end\": 2582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9924047076384382, \"rank\": 0.0076534017498506605, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}, {\"begin\": 2609, \"end\": 2621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's spoken about being initially banned from boxing by her dad who said it wasn't for girls.\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2746, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The attacks on her show that transphobia does not only hurt trans people, but also other women who do not fit conventional ideas of femininity.\\\"\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2891, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2776, \"end\": 2787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transphobia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"transphobia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transphobia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transphobia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After years of competing in amateur tournaments, Khelif is suddenly bring scrutinised for her presence in Paris along with Lin Yu-ting of Taiwan.\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 3038, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2999, \"end\": 3004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999358806, \"rank\": 6.420171585969838e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3016, \"end\": 3027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}, {\"begin\": 3031, \"end\": 3037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9998258855400736, \"rank\": 0.0001741380681544044, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lin won IBA world championships in 2018 and 2022, but the governing body withdrew her bronze medal last year because it said she failed to meet unspecified eligibility requirements in a biochemical test.\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3243, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee (IOC) determined that both athletes are eligible to compete in the 2024 Paris Games and released a statement saying that \\\"as with previous Olympic boxing competitions, the gender and age of the athletes are based on their passport.\\\"\", \"from\": 3245, \"to\": 3513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3249, \"end\": 3286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have seen in reports misleading information about two female athletes competing at the Olympic Games Paris 2024,\\\" the statement said, adding that the athletes were victims of a \\\"sudden and arbitrary\\\" decision by the IBA.\", \"from\": 3515, \"to\": 3739, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3735, \"end\": 3738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9984820405386303, \"rank\": 0.001520266483784248, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Taiwan President William Lai Ching-te gave the 28-year-old Lin his public backing, saying on Facebook, \\\"We should stand united and cheer for her.\\\"\", \"from\": 3741, \"to\": 3887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3741, \"end\": 3757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_Republic_of_China\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Taiwan President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_Republic_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_Republic_of_China\"}, {\"begin\": 3758, \"end\": 3769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lai_Ching-te\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"William Lai\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lai_Ching-te\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lai_Ching-te\"}, {\"begin\": 3766, \"end\": 3778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lai_Ching-te\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lai Ching-te\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lai_Ching-te\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lai_Ching-te\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carini said she was not making a political statement or refusing to fight Khelif.\", \"from\": 3889, \"to\": 3970, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3889, \"end\": 3895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999999971969373, \"rank\": 2.803112410885174e-09, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Later, Italian Premier Giorgia Meloni visited Carini, consoling the boxer in a photo shared on Meloni's Instagram page.\", \"from\": 3972, \"to\": 4091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3979, \"end\": 3986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9945497159191811, \"rank\": 0.0054514099907980096, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3995, \"end\": 4009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Meloni\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giorgia Meloni\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Meloni\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Meloni\"}, {\"begin\": 4018, \"end\": 4024, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999999971969373, \"rank\": 2.803112410885174e-09, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know you will not give up, Angela,\\\" Meloni wrote, \\\"and I know one day you will win what you deserve with effort and sweat.\", \"from\": 4093, \"to\": 4218, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a competition that is finally equal.\\\"\", \"from\": 4219, \"to\": 4259, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif was given a huge roar when she came into the North Paris Arena, partly from members of the large Algerian diaspora in the French capital.\", \"from\": 4261, \"to\": 4405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4319, \"end\": 4324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999358806, \"rank\": 6.420171585969838e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 4365, \"end\": 4373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999965222051735, \"rank\": 2.8787852303851284e-06, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 4390, \"end\": 4396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999730082663826, \"rank\": 2.4528019734659202e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif stopped only briefly to talk to reporters afterwards, saying: \\\"It's always satisfying to win in such an important competition, but I remain focused on my goal of a medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 4407, \"to\": 4585, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Al Jazeera English:\", \"from\": 4605, \"to\": 4631, \"entities\": []}]}"